title: Colin.and.Justins.Cabin.Pressure.S01E01.The.Thrill.of.the.Find.W
description:
Colin and Justin's Cabin Pressure

From the big city to the great white north, everyone's favourite design duo Colin and Justin are taking the plunge into cottage ownership. The series follows the boys as they find their perfect rustic escape and do a complete overhaul on it. The pressure mounts as they battle the bugs and their tiny budget to bring their dream to life.

-----


Episode 01: The Thrill of the Find!

After months of searching with friends Cherri and David for a cottage to buy together in Muskoka, it's love at first sight when Colin and Justin discover a 4 bedroom log home on a quiet little lake.
